# Root environment notes
#
# This project currently runs as a single-user/local demo learning coach.
# It does not include production-grade authentication, authorization, user
# isolation, rate limiting, or audit logging by default.
#
# Backend runtime configuration lives in backend/.env.example. Copy that file to
# backend/.env for local development.
#
# TTS is integration-ready but disabled by default. No real TTS provider is
# enabled unless configured.
#
# Core mode works without RAG dependencies. RAG mode requires:
#   cd backend
#   python -m pip install -r requirements-rag.txt
#   ENABLE_RAG=true python -m pytest tests -q -m rag
